{"tid":87176,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]紅事變白事！新郎新婚夜為11萬禮金錘殺妻子","createTime":"2017-01-19T15:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T15:05:58.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f94e3e22ad523bceba5fd927aee8b594e7586ac7","tid":87176,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T15:05:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/bkncn-20170119154338530-0119_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170119%2Fbkncn-20170119154338530-0119_05011_001.html&d=IFw9uHpJ9pOiX7uGL2cN3Av3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=82194055\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170119/bkncn-20170119154338530-0119_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n昨日紅事，今日白事！河南安陽市湯陰縣伏道鎮一名陳姓男子，本月10日與李姓女友結婚後，翌日凌晨1時許因禮金問題爭執，並用鐵錘砸死李女。目前，當地警方已抓捕陳男，正進一步調查案件。<br />\n<br />\n網傳消息指，1988年出生的陳男與年輕1歲的李女日前結婚後，新婚夜當晚陳男為了已支付的11萬元人民幣禮金，與李女爭執，陳某一怒下手持鐵錘砸向李女頭部致其死亡。<br />\n<br />\n過唔到年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}